name: To Hic or not to Hic?
description:
A visual representation of the HENC Discord vote of 22 Nov 2021, to decide on the collective name going forward. 

From: https://discord.com/channels/908672304236625970/912138076569096192/912281970594160651

"Question:
Should we exclude from the next rounds options similar to the Hic et Nunc brand, such as HEN/HIC/HENC/Hic ex nunc etc.?"

Black represents keeping HEN derivatives, white represents excluding derivatives.

NO to HEN derivatives wins the vote.
